Monte Alto first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[1980 United States census]]<ref name=1980CensusTX/> but did not appear in the [[1990 U.S. census]].<ref name=1990CensusTX/> It reappeared as a CDP in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=2000CensusTX/>

